               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā “Book of the Christening” (fols. 3ra-34rb),
                     incomplete
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text I is called Maṣḥafa ṭǝmqat in the incipit (s. <locus target="#3ra">3ra</locus>) and Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā in Additio 2 (s. also Varia).</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
