                        <condition key="deficient">The front board is missing.
 The sewing is
                           damaged.
 The quires are reinforced with parchment guards.
                           Quires III and VI are lose leaves crudely attached to the binding.
                           Some fols. are held together by stitch repairs.
 The fols. are
                           worn.
 Some fols. are missing.
 Some fols. are stained with wax
                           and dirt.
 A tear is carefully amended on fol. 1.</condition>
