                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Careful</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red.</seg>
                        <date>18th - mid-9th century (?)</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>ይብ፡ ካህ፡ (<locus target="#4rb">4rb</locus>) or ይበ፡ ካ፡ (<locus target="#4vb">4vb</locus>) for ይብል፡ ካህን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the supplicant; incipit of
                           Text I; directives to the ministers; the abbreviation; titles of the
                           books to be read; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic
                           numerals. 
 On the incipit page of Text I (fol. 3r), two lines are
                           rubricated (alternating with a black line).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#34va">f. 34va</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#34va">34va</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ገበዞ፡ ወቄሰ፡
                              ገበዝሂ፡ ወልደ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ለዘጸሐፋ፡ ወለዘአጽሐፋ፡ ለዘቲ፡ መጽሓፍ፡ ሀቦሙ፡ ዓስበ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡
                              ኢትርስኡኒ፡ በጸሎትክሙ፡ ፩፩፡ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/> The note mentions that the Ms. is in the
                           possession of (the church of) Māryām Gäbäzo and that the qes gabaz<note>
                              is Walda Ḥawāryāt. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#34vb">f. 34vb</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#34vb">34vb</locus>: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ክርስትና፡ ዘደብረ፡ ማርያም፡
                              ሐሬነት፡ ወለጠራዚሁኒ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note mentions that the Ms. belongs to the church Dabra Māryām
                              Ḥarennät and that the binder of the Ms. is Gabra Māryām. The word
                              ṭärrazi corresponds to the Amharic word ṭärraž meaning “one who sews”
                              (s. KaneDic2:2122). </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title መፅሐፋ፡ [sic] ጥምቀት፡ is crudely written in pen on
                              <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>.
 - The title መፅሐፈ፡ ጥምቀት፡ is
                           crudely written in pen on <locus target="#35v">35v</locus>.
 -
                           Doodles: <locus target="#2r">2r</locus>.</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
